{"tid":513591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會諗自己會點死","createTime":"2017-12-29T16:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T16:25:31.000Z","uid":139934,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d04cb057a89e186617d649292add9727872f3d45","tid":513591,"uid":139934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個人都會經歷生老病死<br />\n好命嘅就經歷哂四個階段 唔好命嘅可以直接死喺呀媽個肚入面<br />\n咁講好似好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正冇人可以永生 生存到最後都離唔開死 只係時間嘅問題<br />\n唔好當我痴撚線 我純粹覺得呢樣野好值得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 永遠唔會有答案 真係會到臨死一刻先揭盅"},{"pid":"efee6d203810b6a8c6675e41b7a7ab18a655b41a","tid":513591,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb17c00a1450fc183fe20a800fdb68be916342d4","tid":513591,"uid":139934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efee6d203810b6a8c6675e41b7a7ab18a655b41a","tid":513591,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"以前感冒都可以死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def0c35e6c1f817b16240f1fda5725def5d80d8a","tid":513591,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:44:06.000Z","msg":"為左份工死"},{"pid":"fbc914bdf4ab6328b82656bc8fb865e65d40a349","tid":513591,"uid":139934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"def0c35e6c1f817b16240f1fda5725def5d80d8a","tid":513591,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:44:06.000Z","msg":"為左份工死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:46:14.000Z","msg":"巴打好大壓力？"},{"pid":"9839debe763a050c8747a6cab98f5d3e77699e0e","tid":513591,"uid":123456,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:48:22.000Z","msg"